BT
/F1 10.50 Tf
0.145 0.169 0.204 rg
1 0 0 1 52.00 442.00 Tm
(Capital gains 3. Other income 4. Return of principal [2]) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10.50 Tf
0.145 0.169 0.204 rg
1 0 0 1 52.00 420.00 Tm
(This tiered approach affects the tax efficiency of distributions to beneficiaries.) Tj
