BT
/F1 10.50 Tf
0.145 0.169 0.204 rg
1 0 0 1 52.00 361.00 Tm
(the estate. However, the charitable deduction offsets this inclusion, resulting in an estate tax) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 10.50 Tf
0.145 0.169 0.204 rg
1 0 0 1 52.00 347.00 Tm
(savings of $3,048,289.06 for the client [3].) Tj
